data.description: Looking for a spacious and comfortable home that will cater to all your needs? Look no further than this beautiful 4 bedroom, 1 bath home located right off of Dixie Highway! This home features a covered front porch where you can relax and enjoy the scenery as you sip on a cup of coffee or read a good book. Inside, you'll find an open concept living room with an open breakfast bar, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying a family meal. The mud room leads to a huge backyard that sits on over half an acre perfect for outdoor activities and includes a 1 car garage for added convenience. The basement provides ample storage space, while the 2 bedrooms on the 1st floor and 2 more upstairs can also be used as an office space for those who work from home. With close proximity to shopping and restaurants, this home is the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this lovely house your new home!
